grexa (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * v0.3.0 polish and responsiveness release.
  * Preserve per-tab result buffers across tab switches.
  * Add Settings auto-save, responsive Search toolbar, and updated icons.

 -- VisorCraft LLC <maintainer@visorcraft.com>  Mon, 18 May 2026 14:00:00 +0000

grexa (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial alpha release.
  * Rust core (search, replace, container adapter, AI HTTP, document
    extraction, encoding detection, settings, history, profiles,
    context preview).
  * CLI: grexa-cli with all search flags, container mode, and shell
    completion / man page generators.
  * Localization framework with English, German, Japanese catalogs.
  * GUI shell is in active development; this package ships the GUI
    binary as a placeholder until Phase 4 lands.

 -- VisorCraft LLC <maintainer@visorcraft.com>  Sat, 16 May 2026 12:00:00 +0000
